docs.title: Commands
docs.text:
• mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project.
  • mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server.
  • mkdocs build - Build the documentation site.
  • mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit.

docs.title: Project layout
docs.text:
mkdocs.yml    # The configuration file.
docs/
    index.md  # The documentation homepage.
    ...       # Other markdown pages, images and other files.

Inline: E=mc^2

Block: $$ \int_{-\infty}^\infty e^{-x^2} dx = \sqrt{\pi} $$

As shown by Einstein (Hung et al., 2016)[^hung2016quantum], spacetime is relative.

docs.title: References
docs.text: [^hung2016quantum]: Hung, N. T., Hasdeo, E. H., Nugraha, A. R., Dresselhaus, M. S., & Saito, R. (2016). Quantum effects in the thermoelectric power factor of low-dimensional semiconductors. Physical Review Letters, 117(3), 036602.
